sentence.text: However, because dicumarol did not affect well-known apoptosis inducers, such as anti-osteoblast differentiation IgG, tumor necrosis factor (protein import into nucleus, translocation)-a, TNF-related apoptosis-inducing ligand, UV-B and H2O2 of HeLa cells at all, we concluded that regulation of cellular amino acid metabolic process-related intracellular reduction of CoQ, or its reduced product, ubiquinol, may participate in the apoptosis induction of HeLa cells
